Interface Quest<T extends Quest>

  • Type Parameters:

    public interface Quest<T extends Quest>
extends Prototype<T>, Observer<org.spongepowered.api.event.Event>, com.atherys.core.views.Viewable
    Common interface for all Quest classes.
    A Quest represents a series of tasks ( Objectives ), which once completed will reward the player with Reward(s). A completedQuest may optionally contain Requirements which the player must fulfill prior to starting work on the objectives.
